These are Puzzles for 1x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, bike, boat, scooter, roller
1. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2  |   3   |   4   |  5  |
| Transport   | boat | skateboard | scooter | bike | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, march, june, april, october
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |     3     |     4     |     5      |
| Birthday   | april | october | march | january | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, satire, drama, spy, action
1. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
3. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |  3   |     4      |   5   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | drama | zombie | spy | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, traveling, gardening, woodworking, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1       |     2     |       3        |   4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | woodworking | traveling | gardening | video-games | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, mirinda, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |  2   |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | mirinda | 7up | fanta |

