2. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
6. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2   |   3   |  4   |     5      |
| Beverage   | cola | lemonade | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | mirinda |

